select
    {"prop": "a.recipe", "as": "recipe"},
	sum ({"prop": "a.like"}) as like,
	sum ({"prop": "a.dislike"}) as dislike
from
    {"model": "t.recipe.like", "alias": "a"}
group by
	{"prop": "a.recipe"}

select
    {"prop": "a.recipe", "as": "recipe"},
	count (*) as num
from
    {"model": "t.recipe.comment", "alias": "a"}
group by
	{"prop": "a.recipe"}
